data.description: Move-in ready! Built in 2019, this four bedroom, three bathroom home is located in a gated community, close to I-10, and in the award winning Vail School District! Great room floor plan with premium vinyl flooring thought out living areas and the primary bedroom, which is located on the ground floor! Upstairs you will find three spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom with double vanity. Large backyard with covered patio. Garage is equipped with 240 outlet. Wonderful gated community with a Pool, Spa, Park, Gym, Basketball Court and more!
